Features supported
------------------

Lexical:
  + comments
  + single quotes
  + double quotes
  + parameter expansions
  - command substitutions
  - arithmetic expansions
  + line continuations
  - here-docs

Syntactical:
  + simple commands
  + pipelines
  + and/or lists
  + asynchronous/sequential lists
  + brace groups
  + subshells
  + for loops
  - case conditionals
  + if conditionals
  - while loops
  - until loops
  - function definitions
